{"word":"G4327 - προσδέχομαι - prosdéchomai - pros-dekh'-om-ahee - Accept","slug":"G4327","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">προσδέχομαι</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>prosdéchomai"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>pros-dekh'-om-ahee"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Accept"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x03C0;&#x03C1;&#x03BF;&#x03C3;&#x03B4;&#x03B5;&#x0301;&#x03C7;&#x03BF;&#x03BC;&#x03B1;&#x03B9; - prosdechomai</b> - <i>pros-dekh'-om-ahee</i><p/>From <a href=\"#/G4314\">G4314</a> and <a href=\"#/G1209\">G1209</a>; to <i>admit</i> (to intercourse, hospitality, credence or (figuratively) endurance); by implication to <i>await</i> (with confidence or patience): - accept, allow, look (wait) for, take."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/G1184\">G1184</a>, <a href=\"#/G1209\">G1209</a>, <a href=\"#/G1403\">G1403</a>, <a href=\"#/G1523\">G1523</a>, <a href=\"#/G1561\">G1561</a>, <a href=\"#/G2144\">G2144</a>, <a href=\"#/G553\">G553</a>, <a href=\"#/G587\">G587</a>, <a href=\"#/G588\">G588</a>, <a href=\"#/G594\">G594</a>"}]}